GEANT4 simulation tools

A) Batch mode:

 1) With no flag:
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -b  -out 12C_C_200_1 -nev 10000 -exp 12C_200 -run 1

 2) With a given physics list:
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -b  -out 12C_C_200_1 -nev 10000 -exp 12C_200 -run 1 -phys [BIC, BERT or INCL]

 3) With only fragmented events:
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -b  -out 12C_C_200_1 -nev 10000 -exp 12C_200 -run 1 -frag


B) Interactive mode :
 - command:
 TAGsimulation -exp 12C_200 -run 1
